                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920523-59-off342 t17920523-59-crimeloc346"></join>; I lost the things on a Saturday morning at 4 o'clock; I was asleep in bed up two pair of stairs in the shop; he came to work at 4 o'clock in the morning; he had been at work five days before I missed the breeches from the top of my master's loom; the watch was in the window, the money was in my box; he, the prisoner, went away; I missed the things and I followed him; Randal Howard has them.</p>
               <p>
            
